Introduction

Jenyer, or Jiyoon is a South Korean singer and actress under BIXIZ XOUND and Drift Entertainment. She is a member of the trio PRSNT and was a member of the girl group 4minute and their sub-unit 2YOON until their disbandment.

She made her official solo debut on November 2, 2016 with the single "Day and Night".
